{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/5-tempat-terseram-di-jepang-ini-pasti-bikin-kamu-merinding/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"5 Tempat Terseram di Jepang Ini Pasti Bikin Kamu Merinding!","content":"<p>Cerita yang bergenre horror, film horror, komik horror dan buku lainnya, biasanya dibuat dengan tujuan untuk menghibur orang yang membacanya ataupun mengkonsumsinya. Beberapa orang bahkan  menganggap kalau film atau cerita horror itu hanya fiksi atau karangan belaka. Tapi tahu gak sih ?! Tidak semua cerita, film, ataupun komik horror hanya karangan atau fiksi karya sang penulis, nyatanya penulis tersebut terinspirasi dari berbagai mitos dan tempat – tempat seram yang ada. Seperti 5 tempat terseram di Jepang berikut ini !</p>\n<p><strong>1. Hutan Aokihagara</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_11136\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11136\" data-attachment-id=\"11136\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-tempat-terseram-di-jepang-ini-pasti-bikin-kamu-merinding/attachment/9-29/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/9-15.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(akibanation.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(akibanation.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/9-15.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/9-15.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11136\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/9-15.jpg\" alt=\"(akibanation.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-11136\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(akibanation.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Hutan Aokihagara ini sangat terkenal sebagai tempat bunuh diri nomor 1 di Jepang. Lebih dari 500 orang melakukan bunuh diri di Hutan Aokihagara, bahkan di sekitar Hutan Aokihagara sampai dipasang papan larangan untuk melakukan bunuh diri di hutan tersebut. Salah satu film terkenal yang disutradarai Jason Zada yaitu film “ The Forest” juga menggunakan latar belakang Hutan Aokihagara.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>2. Terowongan Tua Chusetsu Fukioka</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_11130\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11130\" data-attachment-id=\"11130\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-tempat-terseram-di-jepang-ini-pasti-bikin-kamu-merinding/attachment/2-1-24/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-19.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(pulangkerja.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(pulangkerja.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-19.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-19.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11130\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/2-1-19.jpg\" alt=\"(pulangkerja.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-11130\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(pulangkerja.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Terowongan tua ini sangat populer dengan suasana mencekam seperti jeritan, tangis dan rintihan saat malam hari.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>3. Oiran Buchi, Yamanashi</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_11133\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11133\" data-attachment-id=\"11133\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-tempat-terseram-di-jepang-ini-pasti-bikin-kamu-merinding/attachment/5-73/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-37.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(justjapanstuff.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(justjapanstuff.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-37.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-37.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11133\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/5-37.jpg\" alt=\"(justjapanstuff.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-11133\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(justjapanstuff.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pemandangan sekitar Oiran Buchi ini sangat indah. Siapa sangka bahwa tempat yang sangat indah ini menyimpan masa lalu kelam. Oiran Buchi, Yamanashi ini konon katanya merupakan tempat terjadinya pembunuhan lebih dari 50 oiran (yang artinya wanita malam). Oiran Buchi ini akan terasa sangat mencekam dan mengerikan saat malam hari.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>4. Gunung Hakone, Tokyo</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_11139\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11139\" data-attachment-id=\"11139\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-tempat-terseram-di-jepang-ini-pasti-bikin-kamu-merinding/attachment/13-12/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/13-4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(japanese stasion)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(japanese stasion)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/13-4.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/13-4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11139\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/13-4.jpg\" alt=\"(japanese stasion)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-11139\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(japanese stasion)</p></div></p>\n<p>Gunung Hakone, Tokyo ini merupakan salah satu tempata wisata yang paling terkenal.  Jika ada pengunjung yang berani  berjalan atau melewati gunung ini saat malam hari akan mendengar suara aneh seperti jeritan, tangisan dan rintihan.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>5. Terowongan Gridley, Yokosuka</strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_11142\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-11142\" data-attachment-id=\"11142\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-tempat-terseram-di-jepang-ini-pasti-bikin-kamu-merinding/attachment/15-10/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/15-2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"(pulangkerja.com)\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;(pulangkerja.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/15-2.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/15-2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-11142\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/15-2.jpg\" alt=\"(pulangkerja.com)\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-11142\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">(pulangkerja.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Konon katanya terowongan Gridley ini dihuni oleh arwah samurai dari Jepang. Bagi kamu yang penasaran dengan sosok hantu samurai bisa mengunjungi terowongan Gridley ini.</p>\n<p>Bagaimana? Apa kalian berani berkunjung ke tempat ini? Bagi kalian yang suka dengan hal yang berbau horror, yuk kepoin aja <a href=\"https://ciayo.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">CIAYO Comics</a> yang juga punya komik horor online dan ga kalah seram dengan 5 tempat horror yang ada di atas. Langsung aja meluncur ke <a href=\"https://ciayo.com/comic/the-other-side\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">sini</a>!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"1b3b3a90-1c4a-5483-958c-08f4e19f59a5"}}}